r-it-starts.md)有关详细信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="430cd-106">See [How to: Use Event Triggers to Control a Storyboard After It Starts](~/docs/framework/wpf/graphics-multimedia/how-to-use-event-triggers-to-control-a-storyboard-after-it-starts.md) for more information.</span></span>  
  
